# Brand Logos

- **Eightfold logo** (navbar/title bar): `/public/eightfold-logo.png` — used as `<img>` in `Navbar.tsx`
- **AI Interview logo** (panel header): `/public/ai-interview-logo.png` — used as `<img>` in `AIInterviewPanel.tsx`

When adding new views or layouts that need branding, reuse these assets from `/public/`.
